<!-- ─── WHAT IS IT ─── -->
<section id="what">
  <h2>What Is Devin AI?</h2>
  <div class="prose section-lead">
    <p>Devin is an <strong>autonomous AI software engineer</strong> built by Cognition Labs. Unlike copilot-style assistants that autocomplete code inside an editor, Devin is a full agent — it plans, writes, tests, debugs, and submits PRs with minimal human intervention. It runs inside its own sandboxed cloud environment (the "Devbox") equipped with a shell, code editor, and browser.</p>
    <p>Devin 2.0 (April 2025) dropped pricing from $500/month to $20/month, introduced Interactive Planning, Devin Search, Devin Wiki, and multi-agent parallel sessions. By late 2025, it had merged hundreds of thousands of PRs across thousands of companies including Goldman Sachs, Santander, and Nubank.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="tag-row">
    <span class="tag">compound AI system</span>
    <span class="tag">multi-model swarm</span>
    <span class="tag">sandboxed execution</span>
    <span class="tag">async delegation</span>
    <span class="tag">SWE-bench 13.86%</span>
    <span class="tag">~$4B valuation</span>
  </div>
</section>

